data.title: SIGNED PHOTO by Simeon Saxe-Coburg-Gotha: Fine No Binding SIGNED PHOTO
data.meta_description: SIGNED PHOTO - No Binding - Condition: Fine - Color Photo (on 6"x 4" card) -- SIGNED by Simeon Saxe-Coburg-Gotha (signature and 2008 date in silver ink). Smeon is a Bulgarian politician who reigned as the last tsar of the Kingdom of Bulgaria as Simeon II from 1943 until 1946, and as Prime Minister from 2001-2005. - SIGNED PHOTO

Shipping Terms:

Shipping costs are based on books weighing 2.2 LB, or 1 KG. If your book order is heavy or over-sized, we may request extra shipping. Also: overseas shipments of books valued over $100 may require request for extra postage since they will be shipped by Priority Mail which has tracking. Also: Please be patient since shipping times given are estimates only and delays in postal system (and customs for international orders) are possible--times given are not guaranteed delivery times. Orders over $200 will require signature confirmation with delivery.** Do not ship postal "OverNight Express"**. Also note: Do no accept or ship any item ordered Internationally that is valued under $65 or expensive items valued over $200 (not worth the risk to send expensive items overseas); and do not ship to certain countries due to past delivery problems- especially Central or South America; Africa etc.- overseas orders please contact first.
